tweet.html: RT @USEmbassyCairo: To honor the life and legacy of Jeannette Lafrance, an Office Management Specialist at U.S. Embassy Cairo who tragically died 67 years ago today, Ambassador Jonathan R. Cohen spoke with Jeannette's sole surviving sister Mrs. Alice Plautz in Wisconsin.
